Summary: Bright object, faded outward towards space for 15 seconds
divs: Sighting DetailsStarted as a bright light, unable to tell what it was at all. But it moved quickly outward towards space as the light faded and faded straight out. lasted 15 seconds and my roomate also witnessed it. Was not a star as it was too bright, and not a plane. Was not close enough to tell exact shape as it was way way way out when I first saw it.
